imdb.plot outline: A new music reality television show. The lead protagonist on the show is iconic London music producer, John Ravenhall, who is launching a new record label, Johnny Boy Records and Entertainment, based out of London. The television show will feature some of the top up and coming acts from America, England and Spain and will chart the launch of the record label following John through the trials and tribulations of running a modern day record company and signing and developing bands.
